Mr. Kenneth A. BronfinHearst Interactive MediaNew York, NYIn 1996, joined Hearst Corp. as SVP and deputy group head of Hearst Interactive Media. Previously spent 10 years with National Broadcasting Co. (NBC), where he held numerous positions, including VP of NBC Cable and Business and Development, general manager of NBC's digital television group, and founder of the company's interactive media unit. 2008 First QuarterAdded to: Hasbro Inc. - Pawtucket, RIHasbro provides children's and family leisure entertainment products. Revenues are $5 billion.















 















 








 




